com.ansca.corona.permissions

Class PermissionsServices.PermissionGroup

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ansca.corona.permissions.PermissionsServices.PermissionGroup
  • Enclosing class:
    PermissionsServices

    public static class PermissionsServices.PermissionGroup
extends Object
    API Level independent constants for supported permission-group names. These constants can be used regardless of the API Level of the device.

    Documentation for each constant elaborates further on the documentation provided by Google. Added in daily build 2016.2828.

    See Also:
    Permission Groups and Manifest.permission_group
